  "types": {
    "StarknetOsConfigHash": {
      "typeCaster": "Mapping",
      "arg": {
        // Reproduce future OS config hashes before adding them to this mapping:
        // 1. Checkout the starkware-libs/sequencer revision matching the deployed OS. For the
        //    current value use tag APOLLO-0.14.3-RC.11, commit
        //    5114457ad4b5d6d1764b520dfa40b9e826f48854.
        // 2. Read the field order and hash version in
        //    crates/apollo_starknet_os_program/src/cairo/starkware/starknet/core/os/os_config/os_config.cairo.
        //    The equivalent Rust function is OsChainInfo::compute_os_config_hash in
        //    crates/starknet_api/src/core.rs.
        // 3. Obtain the chain ID and STRK fee-token address from the matching deployment config.
        //    The current values are in deployments/sequencer/configs/overlays/hybrid/mainnet/common.yaml
        //    and deployments/sequencer/configs/overlays/hybrid/common/common.yaml.
        // 4. For V4, hash [felt("StarknetOsConfig4"), felt(chain_id), fee_token_address]. If the
        //    state-diff-encryption public-key list is nonempty, append its Blake2Felt252 hash.
        //    Blake2Felt252 encodes a felt below 2**63 as two big-endian u32 limbs and any larger
        //    felt as eight big-endian u32 limbs with the high marker bit set. Serialize each limb
        //    little-endian, apply Blake2s-256, then interpret the digest little-endian modulo the
        //    Stark field prime 2**251 + 17 * 2**192 + 1.
        // 5. Compare the decimal result with Starknet.configHash() and add a label only after they
        //    match. Unknown mapping values deliberately remain visible as raw hashes.
        // Current preimage: ["StarknetOsConfig4", "SN_MAIN",
        // 0x04718f5a0fc34cc1af16a1cdee98ffb20c31f5cd61d6ab07201858f4287c938d], no public keys.
        // Expected hex: 0x05b3bc83b3a47231aa5f15e73309ef7e09e087bd4ace767656fe5d713f6e2d7a.
        "2579130946496422157802313572919622021390761807038780433165936715591440018810": "Starknet OS config V4 (SN_MAIN, STRK fee token, no state-diff encryption)"
      }
    }
  },
  "overrides": {
